title: Grunwald to bring new look to city
text: Grunwald to bring new look to city Anna Hartley | 14th Oct 2015 12:00 PM Anna Hartley Journalist I come from a small town called Peak Crossing and grew up in the country. I love the community atmosphere close-knit towns like Peak Crossing and Ipswich have. I firmly believe that everyone has a story to tell and my favourite part about journalism is meeting new and interesting people and sharing their stories. Send any news tips to anna.hartley@qt.com.au
